{"tid":1229304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：政府暫緩修例是公義敗給政治","createTime":"2019-06-16T01:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:55:27.000Z","uid":20933,"like":15,"dislike":1437,"uniUserReply":122,"replies":[{"pid":"ff96656f2cb9904875c1d1e5a381fa34ba51ac2b","tid":1229304,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員湯家驊，出席本台節目時表示，政府決定暫緩修訂逃犯條例，他作為律師和非常相信法治的人，對事件的發展感到失望，形容是「社會公義輸了一仗給政治」。他指香港社會出現大問題，錯誤訊息容易傳遍本港，而市民誤解修例內容的程度令他吃驚。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊指，他作為行會成員，有責任向特區政府反映民意，但承認自己低估了修例的政治問題，由始至終只由律師及法律角度去看待，意識不到政治力量有強大威力。他又批評有法官參與聯署反對修例，認為相關法官應辭職，質疑他背棄整個法律制度及法治原則，亦背棄港人信任。"},{"pid":"756176cce6fdcb0e1d82003b1afa01213e02d7b5","tid":1229304,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:31:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1124638&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1124638%26csid%3D261_341&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=ae455a0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1124638&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"160f0de58f1ff9138723f50e447b1145d155e8f5","tid":1229304,"uid":42473,"like":371,"dislike":1,"score":370,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:33:23.000Z","msg":"係既十一哥"},{"pid":"203e9654c95758eeb1d3cf50edebc7cebfbf2925","tid":1229304,"uid":196924,"like":443,"dislike":2,"score":441,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:33:41.000Z","msg":"佢本人咪就係公義敗給政治嘅好例子囉<br />\n俾人捉到痛腳就政治投敵，放棄公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192ad2b23afc7559243c9e1664027cd154243322","tid":1229304,"uid":2156,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:33:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"44ef38825001a588d6a136270af5e24628